reviewText: It was very cheap, so I guess I got what I paid for. The video is jerky....
Relaxing video of coral reef aquarium. Brightly colored fish very soothing.
I like the ability to be able to change the scene and sound.

video arrived in excellent condition and within timeslot  given...do not think video amazing but will suffice..did stop and go blank after 1st 10min but restarted and was fine there on in...have not had a chance 2 spend much time viewing..actually want more for summer..in winter I use one that is a virtual fireplace..overall from brief time viewing..like it

This is the most gorgeous coral DVD Ive seen so far. My favorite part is the Coral Reef Film, but the other aquarium tracks are beautiful too. You have your choice of sounds for each of the tracks. I personally don't listen to waves as there wouldnt be any underwater, but thats no reason to lower the rating in the least. Some people like the sounds of waves in any situation. For me, I just chose the music tracks - no problem.  The different music is beautiful and calming. The corals themselves are mesmerizing - I couldn't take my eyes off the screen. Add in the vibrant tropical fish of many hues (ie: the clown fish) and the colors just hypnotize me into such a relaxed and tranquil state that everything else seems to go away. Yet another great video with amazing photography for the Helsloot company. Great Job once again!

This is a pretty video when u r tired of watching tv and just want a relaxing video to watch or have on when entertaining
friends.
Vibrant colors, serenity, and my cat loves it!  What more could on want?  Sure beats a big, dark screen.  Treat yourself!

I gave this to my elderly mother as a gift.  She loves this DVD.  It lets her enjoy the look and sounds of an aquarium without the maintenance. She puts it on while reading, cleaning, or just relaxing.  It adds some color and "life" to her home.
Excellent dvd which is suitable if you want to be able to relax in front of the TV and you love fish.
